title: This service can share your personal information to third parties
quoteText:
We may also share certain information such as your location, browser, cookie data, and other data relating to your use of our Service with our business partners to deliver advertisements (“ads”) that may be of interest to you.
wikiHow may allow third-party ad servers or ad networks to serve advertisements on the Service.
